Best Choice: Implementation Consultant

This is the closest role to an Odoo Functional Consultant.

Daily Work
Understand client requirements
Configure Odoo
Create workflows
User training
Testing (UAT)
Go-live support
Documentation
Remote meetings with clients

Most implementation partners allow hybrid or remote work after training.

🥈 Business Support Analyst

This is another excellent role.

Daily Work
Support existing ERP customers
Solve Odoo issues
Configure modules
Help customers via:
Email
Zoom
Google Meet
Teams
Document solutions

This role is commonly offered as remote support because everything can be done online.

🥉 Customer Support Analyst (ERP)

Typical responsibilities:

Handle support tickets
Troubleshoot module issues
Guide users
Escalate technical bugs
Provide training

This is also a good entry point into functional consulting.

